        <div class="training-card"><div class="training-card-title">Wear</div><div class="training-card-desc">Apparel built to perform in training and carry the same standard into the rest of life.</div><div class="service-arrow" style="margin-top:1rem;"><a href="{{ shop_url }}">Shop AREN</a></div></div>
